  <brief_title>T-Cell Vaccination in Multiple Sclerosis (MS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of T-Cell Vaccination in Multiple Sclerosis - Phase I/II Safety and Efficacy Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
